        "setup": "Create an account on the [Experian Global Developer portal](https://developer.experian.com/) and register an application from [Get Started](https://developer.experian.com/get-started). The portal states that when you register an application, a `Client ID` and `Client Secret` are created for making API calls. Use those app credentials to obtain access tokens as described in the [OAuth 2.0 tutorial](https://developer.experian.com/tutorials/oauth-20-tutorial)."
